name: Shodagor Katari-Nazir Rice
description: Shodagor Katari-Nazir rice is white & extra long in size, has a beautiful aroma. Its properties have a high nutritious value. Because of its long grains, it is easy to digest.

name: Chashi Aromatic Chinigura Rice
